description: This stunning back corner unit boasts over 1,500 square feet of beautifully designed living space, illuminated by natural light streaming through 14 windows. Bask in all-day sunshine or unwind on your spacious private deck—ideal for both relaxing and entertaining. You'll also enjoy access to a generous common roof deck offering panoramic city views. Inside, the open-concept layout features a stylish beverage bar complete with a built-in wine fridge, making it perfect for hosting. Both bedrooms include oversized closets, providing plenty of storage. The primary suite is a true retreat, with enough space to accommodate a home office or cozy reading nook.Additional perks include garage parking and unbeatable proximity to everything the city has to offer. This one is not to be missed! 2nd garage parking space is rented but paid for the year. If you would like to keep it, $300 a month. The building offers a dog run off the lobby for the cold winter nights!
